These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, apricot, mauve, red
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, r&b, salsa, techno
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, puzzles, cooking, fishing
House: ranch-style, townhouse, farmhouse, tower
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the fan of techno##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who likes mauve and the person who likes red##2
3. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the ranch-style house##1
4. the tower house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
5. the fan of metal is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
6. the farmhouse house is the person who likes mauve##1
7. the fan of r&b is on the left of the person who likes red##1
8. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far right##1
9. the person who likes apricot is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Color   | apricot | red   | amber  | mauve  |
| Music-Genre   | r&b    | techno    | metal      | salsa    |
| Hobby   | fishing | puzzles | cooking | board-games |
| House     | tower  | ranch-style       | townhouse    | farmhouse     |

