.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, singing, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, sunflower, bellflower, balloon-flower
4 different games are played: canasta, whist, chess, poker
There are 4 different nationalities: american, colombian, italian, pakistani
1. the pakistani is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
3. the person playing poker is the colombian##1
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person playing chess and the american##2
6. the pakistani is between the person who growsballoon-flower and the person playing poker##2
7. the person playing canasta is on the far right##1
8. the person who growssunflower is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
9. the person who growsbellflower is on the right of the person playing whist##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Hobby         | woodworking | drawing    | singing  | cooking    |
| Flower   | azalea      | sunflower  | balloon-flower  | bellflower |
| Game           | poker      | chess       | whist      | canasta       |
| Nationality         | colombian    | pakistani | italian | american |

