7. the person who likes blue is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
8. the person who likes grey is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
9. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who likes purple and the townhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
