 2. the person driving the bike is the person who growsrose##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the bike is the person traveling to colone##1
 6. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person driving the scooter is the person who growstulip##1
 8. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 9. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person who growsdaffodil##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Flower           | rose  | daffodil | daisy     | tulip |
| Transport   | bike | bus  | trike | scooter       |
