 2. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is the fan of electronic##1
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the fan of funk##1
 6. the fan of techno is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the person drinking tea is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the fan of techno is between the owner of the cat and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Music-Genre          | electronic         | techno         | ambient     | funk      |
| Beverage           | lemonade | tea | cola    | hot-chocolate     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Pet         | guinea-pig     | turtle       | cat | goat |

